    <briefdescription>
<para>SDP attribute value container structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Structure that holds a parsed attribute value of any supported type. The type field indicates which member of the union contains the actual value. This structure provides a unified way to handle different types of SDP attribute values after parsing. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
